  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">South Africa is The Rape Capital of the World - say Interpol - where 1/3rd of all females have been or will be Raped. The Joe Slovo Foundation got fed up with people talking lots BUT doing little, so we are rolling a Mobile Rape Rescue Alarm Service for girls &amp; women to press when they feel in danger that instantly sends multiple alarm messages to local community, family and friends with their location so they can respond urgently; prevent the rape&amp; catch the rapist.</narrative>
  </description>
